sentences: Mollo's first band was Crossbones, which he joined in 1981 and found some degree of success in their native Italy.
In 1986, Mollo met English producer Kit Woolven, who produced his first album in 1989, followed by a tour across Europe.

During this time, Mollo continued to write and record his own music and, after being introduced to Tony Martin in 1998, released The Cage with him in 1999.
